lenders.loan_because:
Loaning to the the causes that the good people at Kiva have presented to the world is one of the things that I find most fantastically satisfying in my entire life. People all too often forget to give to others and ask nothing in return. It's one of the strange and wonderful things about the human species that we get oh so much joy from helping others selflessly but sadly do not do so nearly enough.

I love Kiva most of all though because it let's me give those that both need it the most but also those that are prepared to do what they must to make the most of the help that backers give them when they loan through Kiva. It is far too difficult to feel like you are able to contribute to making a difference to the world around us. When I first discovered Kiva I was more excited than you could possibly imagine due to previously feeling so utterly powerless to change the things that make me sad in the world and now thanks to Kiva I am one step closer to that dream.
